{"tid":2195503,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"手足各位借個位　唔好意思阻住你","createTime":"2020-09-09T08:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T10:41:38.000Z","uid":73381,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"994e22b6d3718d170a82b42891c872a3cd3bc54e","tid":2195503,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:26:47.000Z","msg":"手足各位借個位　唔好意思阻住你<br />\n望前看　想像世上只有想不通的人<br />\n沒有走不通的路 沒有絕望的處境<br />\n只會有處於絕望的人 鄭松泰<br />\n<br />\n如果連大家都要放棄<br />\n香港還需說什麼未來<br />\n鄭松泰　何時跑步未必是最快<br />\n至少他從來都不後退<br />\n<br />\n因為世上大概只　有我們是香港人<br />\n必須靠港人為大<br />\n要票投五號　鄭松泰鄭松泰泰博<br />\n<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=692309e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網"},{"pid":"7b20c7adcefa830fd3d7d60878ba70187ecf2612","tid":2195503,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:27:19.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世上只有想不通的人，沒有走不通的路。<br />\n世上沒有絕望的處境，只有處於絕望的人。 如果連你都放棄，香港還需要說什麼未來?<br />\n我未必跑得最快，但從不後退。<br />\n因為，世上只有我們是香港人。<br />\n港人為大，票投五號，鄭松泰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qJz67rjXJJA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqJz67rjXJJA&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=a0fe6dd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qJz67rjXJJA</a>"},{"pid":"7af994335f50d6c7fab1121d1da618405a15a9b7","tid":2195503,"uid":8968,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:27:32.000Z","msg":"收爺啦7頭 日日係到蟲泰蟲泰"},{"pid":"869eff5d8744875a2f354f965567115601c6f54f","tid":2195503,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7b5992cb866b1db7f7cc86eaea7e42e84ec192","tid":2195503,"uid":366773,"like":4,"dis